thread.title: Gen Li
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Gen Li

author: Gen Li
title: Gen Li
text: I was sending a parcel to China and they were using DHL as their carrier. DHL never disappoint me whether this time or my previous dealings with them. Not sure if PACK&SEND use DHL as their carrier if you are sending to other countries but at lease this time I am very happy with the experience.
